        <section class="section">
            <h2>Navigation Menu</h2>
            <p>The top navigation bar provides quick access to all major sections of the application. With clearly labeled links, users can easily find what they need without confusion.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="section">
            <h2>Interactive Elements</h2>
            <p>Buttons, forms, and other interactive elements are designed to be accessible and easy to use. All actions are clearly labeled and provide immediate feedback to enhance usability.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="section">
            <h2>Customizable Settings</h2>
